{"type": "article", "id": 18078, "title": "宇宙飞船积木", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-26T07:20:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 66, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125730F6QevalYRJfESOPA.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这套可以拼成宇宙飞船的积木似乎是为尚有童心的成人准备的，来自纽约的 Huzi Design。他们用实心榉木模拟太空飞船等零件，通过特殊的磁力系统直接吸附搭配。一套积木共有 28 块零件和 58 个连接点，有银色、黑色和原木色三种，拼接后小型飞船比普通的玩具更有质感，可以变成有趣的办公室的点缀。<a href=\"http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/cindyng/cosmos-timeless-magnetic-wooden-toys\" target=\"_blank\">这里是众筹链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021257274XUlK15xF2WYbmdV.gif\" width=\"680\" height=\"680\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125729OD8S4xlgFKRI3Nuw.jpg\" width=\"472\" height=\"629\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.33262712\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125729DiCpEM23roFWqkyO.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"718\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74791667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021257309CPmfAegKHzL1wkF.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"872\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.80740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}